{
  "stem": "23942.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a preview what was coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they are-- how they knew this, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I heard this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when I heard this, at that moment, I didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I didn't ask nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I walked home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And from-- and as I'm sitting there in that-- it was called [POLISH] in Polish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this is where you got your delicious ice cream, if there was in the-- one place where you got your ice cream.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a fun place for a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I loved to visit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But from there on, this-- this was the warning I got.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I made up my mind, hearing-- hearing these words, that at all odds, I'm going to cheat the Germans with their dogs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I am going to somehow find a way to survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was from that moment-- that was the first spark in my head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That I made up my mind-- I'm going to survive this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I was like a child, I was thinking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But I was a very strong child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I had a very special kind of will, I guess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because I made up my mind at that moment that there is no way they are going to kill me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It could have been foolish, but that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I said, I'm going to somehow outwit the dog and the German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I made up my mind, I'm going to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I didn't-- I can't explain to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But I remember, that was the first time that I thought, I'm not going to let myself be killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And sure enough, it was like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Pretty soon-- one day, my grandmother said, we're going-- you see, they told other people to get on a wagon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was the final solution.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
